FBIS4-663 "drafr072_a_94013" FBIS-AFR-94-072 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Rwanda Heavy Fighting Continues; UN Troops Begin Withdrawal Heavy Fighting Continues; UN Troops Begin Withdrawal RPF Notes End of Evacuation Deadline EA1404104094 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura in French to Rwanda 0500 GMT 14 Apr 94 EA1404104094 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura French BFN [Text] The period given by the Rwandan Patriotic Front [RPF] to the international community to evacuate foreign nationals ended a few minutes ago. You know that the deadline was set for 0700. Currently it is 0732 in our studio, therefore, the deadline passed 32 minutes ago.
